---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Coaching Hub Proximity | Jyoti Girls PG near Osmanpura"
  description="Jyoti Girls PG sits near Deogiri College, DIEMS and Osmanpura's leading coaching institutes, giving students more time to study and rest."
>

  <section style="padding: 60px 0 40px; background: var(--color-bg-base);">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Girls PG near Osmanpura</span>
      <h1 class="section-heading">Coaching Hub Proximity &amp; College Access</h1>
      <p class="section-lead">Stay within walking distance of Deogiri College, DIEMS, and Osmanpura's premier institutes for NEET, JEE, and professional courses without compromising on safety.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-white);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Minutes Away from Colleges &amp; Academies</h2>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:20px;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Deogiri College &amp; DIEMS</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">0.8 km walk to Deogiri College and 0.9 km to DIEMS engineering — no daily auto or rickshaw expense.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Aakash &amp; Resonance</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Just a 7-minute walk from Jyoti Girls PG, making early morning batches easy for NEET aspirants.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Allen Career Institute</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Reachable in under 10 minutes with safe, well-lit streets and caretaker-approved paths.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">CA &amp; CS Tutorials</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Popular commerce coaching centres lie within 2 km, with study partners often sharing the same route.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-subtle);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Transport &amp; Support Services</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:20px;max-width:600px;">
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">Evening shuttle for students attending late doubt-solving sessions.</li>
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">GPS-tracked cabs arranged by the PG for early or late-hour classes.</li>
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">Parent alerts for safe arrivals after coaching.</li>
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">Shared study groups arranged by rooms to match class timings.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-white);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Study Benefits of Staying Close</h2>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:20px;margin-bottom:40px;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">More Revision Time</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Students save 60–90 minutes daily and reinvest the time in revision or mentor sessions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Less Travel Stress</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Walking distance avoids crowded buses, reducing fatigue and improving attendance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Greater Accountability</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Caregivers confirm class timings and match them with curfew logs, keeping focus on academics.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <button class="btn-primary" data-modal="visit">Plan a location tour</button>
        <a href="https://wa.me/919922333305?text=Hello%20Jyoti%20Girls%20PG%2C%20help%20me%20understand%20coaching%20commute%20options." class="btn-whatsapp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Discuss commute plans</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
